    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Not a bug, it is pad filling (as the default), which is fill-forward, you can disable by passing `fill_method=None`)\n\n```\nIn [14]: df.pct_change(7,fill_method=None)\nOut[14]: \n            Series\n2013-09-12     NaN\n2013-09-13     NaN\n2013-09-14     NaN\n2013-09-15     NaN\n2013-09-16     NaN\n2013-09-17     NaN\n2013-09-18     NaN\n2013-09-19     NaN\n2013-09-20     NaN\n2013-09-21     NaN\n\n[10 rows x 1 columns]\n\nIn [15]: df.pct_change(7,fill_method='pad')\nOut[15]: \n              Series\n2013-09-12       NaN\n2013-09-13       NaN\n2013-09-14       NaN\n2013-09-15       NaN\n2013-09-16       NaN\n2013-09-17       NaN\n2013-09-18       NaN\n2013-09-19       NaN\n2013-09-20 -0.036649\n2013-09-21       NaN\n\n[10 rows x 1 columns]\n\n```\n"
  },
