    "body": "Hi guys, I think this issue should be re-opened. @selik is absolutely right that \"Errors should never pass silently\" and unless explicitly done so, this _is_ an error. Not technically, as the default is currently fill_method='pad', but that is not an answer. That is just stating the problem. Upgrading this to  fill_method=None is in now way different to deprecating inplace=True, or any other relatively major change that pandas has gone or will go through. "
